Ok, now I had the same problem: to take the rock or to go on attacking? Observe that black has check in b4 that make me lose castle, and my king stays in the center, in a very bad position. After knight f5, my queen has to move. Where? I was taking the game pretty seriously, despite my advantage, and I analyzed this position for a while, finding surprising combinations. I cannot report all of them here, it would be very large. Find them yourself, and have a good time. 

My move was "resigning" to the complicated game that generates from here. Alternatives were: 13 c5, 13 a3, 13 Rc1, 13 Be2, 13. h4...
